metadata.name: The Bigger Picture
metadata.description:
On August 5th, 2022, I captured this picture at 6am ET in Seaview, Fire Island. It has not been edited or touched up. 

What do you see: The sun or the surroundings? 

This was a simple question once posed to me and I saw the sun. In my answer, I realized I was missing the bigger picture.

100% of the Primary Sales from this piece will be donated to New York Cares "Stand with Students" - the largest citywide initiative to help Title I schools.
